attributes.description:
1996 Land Cruiser 80 series 4.2 GX diesel 4x4 (normally aspirated). Manual. 400 000km, 1 previous owner. Reconditioned aircon with new piping etc. All brakes redone. 4x New shocks, all suspension rubbers and control arms replaced. Two new tyres and two 95% left. Complete new exhaust front to back. Replaced synchro on 2nd gear, clutch plate and release bearing almost new. Seats repaired, full valet done. Small section of roof rust repaired and roof resprayed.  
Faults on car: Back door hinges worn, small dent on one door. Rear diff needs new welding in one spot, basically needs repair on previous attempt, it's sweating oil. Speedometer/dashboard needs a good clean. Maybe R10k to spend in total.
Sales team 021-5920943
